                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3348h27t/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>strange that he would get others to join him, but he<lb/> does,\n                                        altho' they condemn his conduct—so every thing<lb/> is going\n                                        to the old way—the Synagogue is badly<lb/> attended, a great\n                                        many remain away <del>that attended</del><lb/> who used to\n                                        come when they could hear a Sermon</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I forgot to state that\n                                                  <persName>Simmonds</persName> never proposes<lb/>\n                                        any thing; if he did &amp; it was good I would not\n                                        hesitate<lb/> to join him;</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The minister of public instruction in<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>Copenhagen</placeName> has stirred into our\n                                        affairs thro' <persName>Dr Levison</persName><lb/> second\n                                        minister of that congregation he is desirous of<lb/> coming\n                                        here. I have sent in my declaration to Government<lb/>\n                                        exposing our situation &amp; wants—which I trust will\n                                        have<lb/> some weight.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">There was no package for me on board<lb/> the\n                                        Radius that brought the Occident for\n                                                  <persName>Simmonds</persName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3348h27t/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
